---
// import background image of target state
import fishing from '../images/fishing-1600.webp'
---

<section class="relative overflow-hidden py-24 md:py-32">
	<!-- Background image with overlay -->
	<div class="absolute inset-0">
		<img
			src={fishing.src}
			alt=""
			class="h-full w-full object-cover object-[40%_center] md:object-center"
		/>
		<div class="absolute inset-0 bg-gradient-to-b from-black/80 via-black/70 to-black/80"></div>
	</div>

	<!-- Content overlay -->
	<div class="relative mx-auto max-w-3xl px-6">
		<div class="space-y-8 text-center">
			<h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white md:text-4xl lg:text-5xl">
				Your Business Should Give You More Freedom, Not Less
			</h2>

			<div class="space-y-6 text-lg text-gray-100">
				<p>
					You want a successful business that runs smoothly without your constant attention. But
					without enough sales, you canâ€™t afford to hire staff and end up doing everything yourself,
					which causes burnout.
				</p>

				<p>
					Rapid Rank helps you get found on Google and convert website visitors into paying
					customers, so you can avoid burnout and enjoy more free time while your business grows.
				</p>
			</div>

			<!-- Simple 3-step process -->
			<div class="mt-12 grid gap-8 text-left md:grid-cols-3">
				<div class="rounded-lg bg-black/30 px-4 py-6 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-400">Step 1</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">15-Min Discovery</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-100">Quick call to understand your business and goals</p>
				</div>

				<div class="rounded-lg bg-black/30 px-2 py-6 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-400">Step 2</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Research & Strategy</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-100">Our 23-point process finds what sets you apart</p>
				</div>

				<div class="rounded-lg bg-black/30 px-4 py-6 backdrop-blur">
					<div class="mb-4 text-sm font-semibold text-indigo-400">Step 3</div>
					<h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-white">Build & Launch</h3>
					<p class="mt-2 text-gray-100">Your lead-generating website goes live</p>
				</div>
			</div>

			<div class="mt-12">
				<button
					class="cta-button inline-flex items-center rounded-lg bg-gradient-to-br from-indigo-500 to-indigo-400 px-4 py-4 text-lg font-semibold text-white shadow-lg transition-all duration-300 hover:from-indigo-600 hover:to-indigo-500 hover:shadow-xl"
				>
					Get Your Custom Growth Plan
				</button>

				<p class="mt-4 text-sm text-gray-200">
					Stop chasing customers. Let the leads flow in while you run your business.
				</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
</section>
